          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The Four Scoping Dimensions"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "AIA scope is defined along four dimensions. Each must be answered before the assessment begins:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
