      },
      {
        "type": "blockquote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "The AIA boundary must include steps 1–5. A narrow scope covering only step 2 would miss discriminatory preprocessing in step 1 and biased score normalization in step 3 — both of which could produce a discriminatory outcome regardless of Claude's own fairness."
              }
            ]
